'''Atomic''' may refer to:
* Of or relating to the [[atom]], the smallest particle of a chemical element that retains its chemical properties * [[Atomic physics]], the study of the atom * [[Atomic Age]], also known as the "Atomic Era" * [[Atomic (magazine)|''Atomic'' (magazine)]], an Australian computing and technology magazine * [[Atomic Skis]], an Austrian ski producer * [[Atom (order theory)]], in mathematics * ''[[Atomic, Living in Dread and Promise]]'', a 2015 documentary by Mark Cousins * The "Atomic Kid" Buddy Wayne, American professional wrestler from [[NWA All-Star Wrestling|All Star Wrestling]]
